SPELL NAME  : Turn Undead
SPELL SYNTAX: Turn <target>
SPELL COST  : Varies
DESCRIPTION : This spell allows the cleric to channel his powers of
              goodness in order to drive away undead creatures.  If
              the cleric is significantly more powerful than the target
              undead creature, it will be crushed under the overwhelming
              power of good the cleric possesses.
              Wisdom also helps in this spell.

